00:44:18,625 --> 00:44:20,100
You should keep it company

937
00:44:20,100 --> 00:44:21,501
and help it get better soon.

938
00:44:32,399 --> 00:44:33,679
God of Wind,

939
00:44:33,679 --> 00:44:34,525
I think Xiaoguai

940
00:44:34,525 --> 00:44:36,050
