966
00:45:37,479 --> 00:45:38,125
Besides,

967
00:45:38,125 --> 00:45:39,239
you join Huangquan Battalion

968
00:45:39,239 --> 00:45:40,560
for the just cause.

969
00:45:41,120 --> 00:45:41,919
Going with you

970
