971
00:45:43,199 --> 00:45:44,325
concerns with the safety of Dazheng.

972
00:45:44,325 --> 00:45:44,875
Yeah.

973
00:45:44,875 --> 00:45:45,919
How can our family not support us?

974
00:45:45,919 --> 00:45:46,600
Yes.

975
00:45:47,040 --> 00:45:47,675
Brother.

